Structural and Concrete -- foundations + steel + slabs
Building Envelope -- walls + roof + glazing + doors
Interior Architectural -- partitions + ceilings + flooring + paint + accessibility + signage + millwork
Mechanical Systems -- HVAC + plumbing + fire protection + exhaust + breathing air + BAS
Electrical Systems -- power + lighting + IT + fire alarm + PA + emergency + solar-ready + service entrance
Site and Civil Works -- earthwork + paving + flatwork + drainage + landscaping
Underground Utilities -- water + sewer + storm + gas + power + telecom + tie-ins + connection fees + environmental
Cold Storage Building -- 6000 sf PEMB complete turnkey
Specialty Equipment -- OH doors + lockers + generator + workshop + misc (excl L-095/L-096 GR transparency lines)
Professional Design Fees -- architectural + civil + structural + mechanical + electrical + building science + environmental + geotech + markup
Bonds + Insurance + Permits -- perf bond + L&M bond + CCIP + builder's risk + CGL + building permit + trade permits + surety fee
Additional Options 1-6 (wash bay + yard lighting + access control + security + signage + FF&E)
GST on base ($493k) + GST on options ($18k)
